<Legal
	lang="en"
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="How defriction collects, uses and protects your personal data."
	lastUpdated="June 19, 2026"
>
	<p>This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>defriction</strong> ("we", "us") collects, uses, and safeguards your information when you visit <a href="https://defriction.org">defriction.org</a> or use our automation services.</p>

	<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
	<p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your name, email address, company, and any details shared when you book a discovery call or contact us. We may also collect limited technical data (browser type, pages visited) through privacy-friendly analytics.</p>

	<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>To respond to your inquiries and schedule discovery calls.</li>
		<li>To design, build, and deliver the automation services you request.</li>
		<li>To improve our website and communicate relevant updates.</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
	<p>We do not sell your personal data. We only share information with trusted third-party tools necessary to operate our services (for example, scheduling and hosting providers), and only to the extent required to deliver our work.</p>

	<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
	<p>We use industry-standard encryption for data in transit. Where possible, we build on <strong>self-hosted infrastructure</strong>, meaning your operational data stays on your own servers or cloud, not ours.</p>

	<h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
	<p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>

	<h2>6. Cookies</h2>
	<p>We use only essential cookies and privacy-respecting analytics. We do not use advertising or cross-site tracking cookies.</p>

	<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
	<p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected by the "Last updated" date above.</p>

	<h2>8. Contact</h2>
	<p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:defriction@defriction.org">defriction@defriction.org</a>.</p>
</Legal>
